      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "chunker is responsible for dividing\nhuge files into smaller chunks ( 4-5\nmb) and only retry those chunks\nwhich is failed while uploading this\nservice is also responsible for\nreconsrtruting files from chunks",
